[[$1467]]--[[$1470]] writes \texttt{LDA [[$B009]],X; STA [[$65B3]]; LDA [[$B089]],X;  % TODO-SYM: $1467 $1470
STA [[$65B4]]} in the stance path.  All four bases used by enemy-A are
\emph{one byte apart per pair}: [[$B009]]/[[$B089]] for the body, [[$B010]]/[[$B090]]
for walk-variant~1, [[$B017]]/[[$B097]] for the stance feet, [[$B01E]]/[[$B09E]]
